NAME: ŻUBRÓWKA BISON GRASS VODKA
DES: This Polish rye-based vodka is flavored with grass from the Białowieża Forest in northeastern Poland, one of the last and largest primeval forests in the world. It is here where Polish bison roam among the grass. The grass is harvested each June or July, dried, and cut to size. The grass is bundled into small batches and the vodka is pressed through capturing its flavor. A single blade of grass is inserted into each bottle. Note: In the US, the vodka, sold as "Zu Vodka", is artificially flavored as coumarin found in the original is not permitted.

NAME: ABSOLUT CITRON
DES: Citron was first launched in 1988, the second flavored vodka in Absolut's portfolio. Taking Absolut's standard vodka made with winter wheat as its base, Citron uses only natural ingredients--lemon primarily although some lime is used. No sugar has been added. It is the quintessential vodka for your Cosmopolitan.

NAME: ABSOLUT VANILLA
DES: Absolut Vanilla launched in 2003. It is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka and natural flavors. No sugar is added.

NAME: RUSSIAN STANDARD GOLD
DES: This bottling in the Russian Standard Vodka portfolio is distilled from 100% Russian winter wheat as are the rest of their vodkas. But this vodka is flavored with Siberian golden root, or ginseng. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: ABSOLUT LIME
DES: Absolut Lime was introduced in January 2017. It is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka as a base with citrus flavor added. No sugar added. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: CÎROC PEACH
DES: First launched in 2012, this flavored vodka from CÎROC uses its flagship grape-based vodka along with peach and other natural flavors. Bottled at 35% or 37.5% ABV depending on your location.

NAME: ABSOLUT MANDRIN
DES: Absolut Mandrin was first released in 1999, the fourth flavor in Absolut's arsenal. It is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka with orange, mandarin, and citrus flavor. No sugar added. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: SMIRNOFF VANILLA
DES: Vanilla is part of Smirnoff's Confections flavored vodka line. It uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. Formerly sold as Twist of Vanilla. Bottled at 30% ABV.

NAME: ST. GEORGE GREEN CHILE VODKA
DES: The multi-step process required for this vodka starts with filling a still with jalapeño, lime peel, and a non-GMO base spirit which passes through a chamber packed with fresh cilantro. The resulting spirit is then separated into parts and individually macerates with even more peppers: Serrano, habanero, red and yellow sweet bell before being carefully blended back together. Then this concoction is lightly-filtered and still maintains a slight green glow.

NAME: SMIRNOFF RASPBERRY
DES: This flavored vodka uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. It is infused with natural raspberry flavors. Bottled at 35% ABV

NAME: GREY GOOSE VX
DES: Released in 2014, VX is a blend of 95% Grey Goose Vodka and 5% cognac. This product is designed to be enjoyed on the rocks or on its own.

NAME: DEEP EDDY CRANBERRY
DES: Deep Eddy is a column-distilled corn-based vodka. Released in 2014, this flavored vodka is the fourth vodka from Deep Eddy. Made with real New England cranberries and pure cane sugar. Deep Eddy Distillery is located in Buda, Texas just outside Austin where the brand's headquarters are located. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: CÎROC PINEAPPLE
DES: First launched in 2014, this flavored vodka uses CÎROC's standard grape-based vodka and adds pineapple and other natural flavors. Bottled at 35% or 37.5% ABV depending on your location.

NAME: CÎROC APPLE
DES: Launched in 2015, this flavored vodka uses CÎROC's standard grape-based vodka and adds apple and other natural flavors. Bottled at 35% or 37.5% ABV depending on your location.

NAME: ABSOLUT PEARS
DES: First introduced in 2007, this vodka is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka with natural pear flavor. No sugar added. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: GREY GOOSE L'ORANGE
DES: L'Orange from Grey Goose is made using real oranges. Its essential oils are added to Grey Goose's standard winter wheat-based vodka.

NAME: DEEP EDDY LEMON
DES: Deep Eddy Lemon Vodka is created using Deep Eddy Vodka as a base, then mixed with real lemon juice. It is lightly sweetened with cane sugar. Deep Eddy Distillery is located in Buda, Texas just outside Austin where the brand's headquarters are located.

NAME: CÎROC FRENCH VANILLA
DES: This flavored vodka first launched in 2017. It uses Cîroc's standard grape-based vodka and adds a blend of vanilla flavors. Bottled at 35% or 37.5% ABV depending on your location.

NAME: ABSOLUT RASPBERRI
DES: First released in 2004, this vodka is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka with natural raspberry flavor. No sugar added. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: KETEL ONE CITROEN
DES: Introduced in 2000, this citrus-flavored vodka is made with the oils of four types of lemons and two types of limes which are added to their winter wheat-based vodka. Two types of lemons from Sicily, one from Spain, one from Guinea, West Africa are used along with two types of limes from the Caribbean.

NAME: SMIRNOFF KISSED CARAMEL
DES: Released in 2012, Kissed Caramel is part of Smirnoff's Confections flavored vodka line. It uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. Bottled at 30% ABV.

NAME: SMIRNOFF GREEN APPLE
DES: This flavored vodka uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. It is infused with natural green apple flavors. Bottled at 35% ABV

NAME: ABSOLUT KURANT
DES: First released in 1992, the third flavor for Absolut after Peppar and Citron. This vodka is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka with natural black currant flavor. No sugar added, it is bottled at 40% ABV. It was originally going to be called "Vinbär", the Swedish name for black currant.

NAME: NEMIROFF HONEY PEPPER VODKA
DES: This Ukrainian vodka is grain-based and flavored with honey, herbs, and red chilies. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: SVEDKA BLUE RASPBERRY
DES: Launched in 2017, this flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural berry and lemon flavors are added to create this sweet and sour vodka. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: CÎROC COCONUT
DES: First released in 2010, this is the first flavor extension for CÎROC. Taking their grape-based flagship vodka, they add coconut and other tropical flavors. Bottled at 35% or 37.5% ABV depending on your location.

NAME: CÎROC MANGO
DES: Launched in 2016, this flavored vodka uses CÎROC's standard grape-based vodka and adds mango and other natural flavors. Bottled at 35% or 37.5% ABV depending on your location.

NAME: DEEP EDDY SWEET TEA
DES: Deep Eddy Sweet Tea begins by using the brand's Original corn-based vodka as its base. It's made with Indonesian whole black tea leaves and is sweetened using organic honey from the Texas Hill Country.

NAME: ABSOLUT PEPPAR
DES: First introduced in 1986, this was Absolut's first--but far from last--flavored vodka. Using their standard winter wheat vodka as its base, natural flavors are added evoking flavors of jalapeño and bell pepper. No sugar added. Kick your Bloody Marys up a notch.

NAME: 44 NORTH MOUNTAIN HUCKLEBERRY
DES: This huckleberry-flavored vodka uses the brand's unflavored vodka made from potatoes as its base. That is distilled from 100% Idaho potatoes, Burbank and Russet, and is naturally gluten-free. It is brought down to 35% ABV using Rocky Mountain water. 44 North is named for the latitude that crosses through Idaho. Try with lemonade or club soda!

NAME: GREY GOOSE CHERRY NOIR
DES: Cherry Noir was first introduced in 2012. It is made with the natural essences of cherries, including black cherries from the French Basque Country. These essences are added to Grey Goose's standard winter wheat-based vodka. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: OYO STONE FRUIT VODKA
DES: This forward-thinking vodka from Ohio pours a fantastic amber-crimson color because of its infusion of Montmorency cherries, yellow peaches, apricots, almonds, hibiscus and a touch of local honey. The base vodka is made of local wheat and distilled no less than 34 times.

NAME: DEEP EDDY LIME
DES: Deep Eddy Lime is made using the brand's Original Vodka (column-distilled corn-based) as the base. This lime flavored vodka is made with real lime juice. Deep Eddy Distillery is located in Buda, Texas just outside Austin where the brand's headquarters are located. Deep Eddy Lime is bottled at 35% ABV. Available as of March 2021.

NAME: ABSOLUT JUICE APPLE EDITION
DES: Absolut Juice Apple Edition was released in summer 2019. It is made with Absolut Vodka and 5% fruit juice. The color is obtained by the natural juice. No artificial flavors are added. Each serving contains just 99 calories per 1.5 fl oz.

NAME: CÎROC BLACK RASPBERRY
DES: This flavored vodka extension from the French vodka brand infuses black raspberry and other natural flavors with their flagship grape-based vodka. CÎROC Black Raspberry is a limited edition released fall 2018, in time for the holiday season.

NAME: EFFEN CUCUMBER VODKA
DES: This is a cucumber infusion of EFFEN’s classic wheat based vodka. The spirit runs through a column still thus achieving great purity and the temperature during the process is kept very low in order to avoid imparting any burnt flavors to the grain. Active carbon plays the last but critical step of filtering the spirit.

NAME: SMIRNOFF WATERMELON
DES: This flavored vodka uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. It is infused with natural flavors. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: GREY GOOSE LA POIRE
DES: La Poire first launched in 2007. It is made with the essential oils of pears including Anjou pear. These essences are added to Grey Goose's standard winter wheat-based vodka. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: FINLANDIA CRANBERRY
DES: This flavored vodka uses the standard Finlandia as its base which is distilled from six-row barley and uses glacial spring water to bring it to proof. First launched in 1994, this cranberry flavored vodka used to be red in color from the berries used in its production. It is now colorless, but fear not. If you are looking for a red colored vodka, seek out Finlandia's Redberry Vodka.

NAME: KETEL ONE ORANJE
DES: Released in 2010, this orange-flavored vodka uses Brazilian and Floridian Valencia oranges and Italian Mandarin oranges in its production. The citrus oils are infused with their standard winter wheat-based vodka. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: SVEDKA CITRON
DES: This citrus-flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural lemon and lime flavors are added. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: SVEDKA STRAWBERRY LEMONADE
DES: First launched in 2014, this flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural strawberry and lemon flavors are added. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: STOLICHNAYA SALTED KARAMEL
DES: Released in 2012 as part of their indulgent vodka series, Salted Karamel is the first salted caramel flavored vodka on the market. It uses Stoli's standard grain-based (wheat and rye) vodka with added flavors. Bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: STOLICHNAYA VANIL
DES: Vanil is Stoli's vanilla-flavored vodka. It is grain based (wheat and rye). Bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: STOLICHNAYA BLUEBERI
DES: First introduced in 2006, this is Stoli's blueberry flavored vodka. Grain based (wheat and rye). Bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: PRAIRIE CUCUMBER VODKA
DES: A Minnesota operation, Prairie spirits buys corn from local farmers to use as the base in all of their spirits. The corn is grown organically and the farmers employ traditional methods to take of invasive weeds such as controlled brush fires as opposed to modern pesticides. The left over grains are used as animal feed for neighboring livestock. With the cucumber infusion natural cucumber flavors are added at the end of distillation.

NAME: SVEDKA MANGO PINEAPPLE
DES: Introduced in 2014, this flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural mango and pineapple flavors are added. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: STOLICHNAYA OHRANJ
DES: Ohranj is Stoli's orange-flavored vodka. Grain based (wheat and rye). Bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: BLAUM BROS. HELLFYRE VODKA
DES: Blaum Bros is a craft distillery housed in Galena, Illinois. A true artisanal affair, the brothers use only local grains that are milled and fermented on location. Hellfyre is created by macerating jalapeños, habaneros, and black peppercorn in their very competent vodka. The vodka is made of wheat and rye and a return to a historic grain-focused style.

NAME: SMIRNOFF LIME
DES: This flavored vodka uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. It is infused with natural lime flavors. Bottled at 35% ABV

NAME: HANGAR 1 BUDDHA'S HAND CITRON VODKA
DES: This citrus-flavored vodka from Hangar 1 is made using grain from the Midwest and Buddha's Hand, also known as a fingered citron. It is very aromatic and has almost no pulp or juice. The distillery is located in a hangar on the grounds of the now-closed Alameda Naval Air Station. Hangar 1 distills a myriad of flavored vodkas, some only seasonally.

NAME: GREY GOOSE LE CITRON
DES: This citrus-flavored vodka is made from natural ingredients. Macerated lemons from Menton, a town on the French Riviera are used as well as citrus oil from Argentine and Brazilian lemons. These two methods yield citrus oil which are blended and added to Grey Goose's standard winter wheat based vodka.

NAME: OYO HONEY VANILLA BEAN VODKA
DES: Made at Middle West Spirits in Columbus, Ohio, this vodka uses its flagship OYO American Character Vodka as its base. That vodka is made from local, soft red wheat. For this bottling, local wildflower honey and single-source, fair-trade, organic vanilla beans are used for flavoring. Bottled at 80 proof unfiltered. Kosher.

NAME: ABSOLUT GRAPEFRUIT
DES: This flavor extension for Absolut launched in summer 2018. As is the case for all Absolut flavors, the brand's standard vodka made from winter wheat forms the base. Natural grapefruit flavor is added to show "the distinct character of pink grapefruit". No added sugar or artificial flavors added. Bottled at 80 proof.

NAME: HANGAR 1 ROSÉ
DES: Created by head distiller, Caley Shoemaker, Hangar 1 Rosé uses real California rosé wine to flavor their classic vodka made from Midwest grains and wine grapes. Bottled at 30% ABV.

NAME: INFUSE SPIRITS MANGO HABANERO VODKA
DES: This California brand infuses real fruits and spices for their flavored vodka. Starting with their unflavored corn-based vodka, they infuse dried red mango and habanero pepper for at least 30 days which you can still see in the bottle. 1.8 g/oz of sugar added. Gluten free. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: 360 DOUBLE CHOCOLATE
DES: This chocolate-flavored vodka is made with natural flavors including sugar. The base vodka is made using locally-sourced corn. 360 Vodka is "eco-friendly", their bottle is made from recycled glass, recycled paper, and printed using eco-friendly ink. Bottled at 35% ABV. Try in a Colorado Bulldog!

NAME: SMIRNOFF WHIPPED CREAM
DES: First released in 2011, Whipped Cream is part of Smirnoff's Confections flavored vodka line. It uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. Bottled at 30% ABV.

NAME: SMIRNOFF BLUEBERRY
DES: This flavored vodka uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. It is infused with natural blueberry flavors. Bottled at 35% ABV

NAME: ABSOLUT CHERRYS
DES: First introduced in 2012, this vodka is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka with cherries, white cranberries, and plum. No sugar added. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: ABSOLUT APEACH
DES: First released in 2005, this vodka is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka with natural peach flavor. No sugar added. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: SMIRNOFF CITRUS
DES: This citrus flavored vodka uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. It is infused with natural citrus flavors. Bottled at 35% ABV. It has been labeled as "Citrus Twist".

NAME: ABSOLUT RUBY RED
DES: First introduced in 2006, Ruby Red is a grapefruit-flavored vodka. It is made with Absolut's standard winter wheat vodka as its base along with natural flavorings. No sugar is added.

NAME: CÎROC SUMMER CITRUS
DES: CÎROC Summer Citrus is distilled from French grapes and infused with natural orange & citrus flavors. It is gluten-free and bottled at 35% ABV. Limited availability begins March 2021.

NAME: ABSOLUT JUICE PEAR & ELDERFLOWER EDITION
DES: Absolut Juice Pear & Elderflower Edition is the third release in the brand's Juice line up following Absolut Juice Apple and Absolut Juice Strawberry. The flavored vodka is made with no artifical flavors or synthetic colors. Each bottle contains 5% real juice in its composition. Bottled at 35% ABV. Available April 2020.

NAME: DEEP EDDY ORANGE
DES: Deep Eddy Orange is made using the brand's gluten free corn-based Original Vodka as its base. Real orange juice is used in its production.

NAME: ABSOLUT JUICE STRAWBERRY EDITION
DES: Absolut Juice Strawberry Edition was released in summer 2019. It is made with Absolut Vodka and 5% fruit juice. The color is obtained by the natural juice. No artificial flavors are added. Each serving contains just 99 calories per 1.5 fl oz.

NAME: CÎROC SUMMER WATERMELON
DES: This flavored vodka from CÎROC uses its flagship grape-based vodka along with watermelon and other natural flavors. It's bottled at 35% ABV and available for a limited time starting in April 2019.

NAME: HANGAR 1 MANDARIN BLOSSOM ORANGE FLAVOUR VODKA
HUMBOLDT'S FINEST HEMP INFUSED VODKA
DES: Humboldt's Finest is infused with a legal food-grade hemp, without any detectable THC, so it's legal in all 50 states. The distillery's USDA certified organic sugarcane-based vodka is the base. Located in Northern California the Humboldt Distillery has access to one of the freshest water sources around a redwood forest.

NAME: INFUSE SPIRITS PEACH VODKA
DES: This California brand infuses real fruits and spices for their flavored vodka. Starting with their unflavored corn-based vodka, they infuse dried freestone peaches for a minimum of 30 days. You can still see them in the bottle. 1.65 g/oz of sugar used. Gluten free. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: CRATER LAKE HAZELNUT ESPRESSO VODKA
DES: Crater Lake Spirits has been in business more than twenty years. In that time they’ve managed to create a wide variety of products. The Hazelnut Espresso Vodka was designed to be a dessert sipper. Crater Lake Vodka is infused with freshly-brewed espresso and hazelnuts. A small amount of cane brown sugar is also added. This is bottled at 25% ABV which makes this not exactly vodka.

NAME: SMIRNOFF SOURS BERRY LEMON
DES: Smirnoff Sours is a line of flavored vodkas consumers are encouraged to drink as shooters (responsibly). The bottles glow in the dark under black light. Bottled at 30% ABV.

NAME: SMIRNOFF ORANGE
DES: This flavored vodka uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. It is infused with natural orange flavors. Bottled at 35% ABV

NAME: FINLANDIA REDBERRY
DES: First launched in 2004 as Redberry Fusion, this flavored vodka gets its color from the berries themselves and not an artificial coloring. This flavored vodka uses the standard Finlandia as its base which is distilled from six-row barley and uses glacial spring water to bring it to proof. Bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: FINLANDIA BLACKCURRANT
DES: First launched in 2009 as Blackcurrant Fusion, this flavored vodka uses the standard Finlandia as its base which is distilled from six-row barley and uses glacial spring water to bring it to proof. Blackcurrant flavors are added and bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: ABSOLUT WILD TEA
DES: First introduced in 2010, This vodka is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka with oolong tea and elderflower flavoring. No sugar added. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: HOPHEAD VODKA
DES: Hophead Vodka is distilled in copper pot stills using two varieties of Willamette Valley hops and grain neutral spirit. Note: In 2017, Anchor Brewing Co. was sold with Anchor Distilling Co. not part of the sale. The distilling company was rebranded as Hotaling & Co. in early 2018 and is still located in Potrero Hill in San Francisco.

NAME: FIREFLY APPLE PIE MOONSHINE
DES: Apple Pie is one of the original 6 Firefly Moonshine flavors released in 2013. It's bottled at 60.3 proof and flavored with apples and cinnamon.

NAME: SMIRNOFF SPICY TAMARIND
DES: Smirnoff Spicy Tamarind is a flavored vodka featuring flavors of tamarind, lime and chiles. As of October 2020, the bottle features glow-in-the-dark packaging. It is bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: JEPTHA CREED HOT PEPPER FLAVORED VODKA
SMIRNOFF ZERO SUGAR INFUSIONS STRAWBERRY & ROSE
DES: This spirit is part of Smirnoff's line of sugar-free vodka infusions. This release is infused with natural flavors of strawberry and rose. It is bottled at a 30% ABV.

NAME: CHASE MARMALADE VODKA
DES: Chase Marmalade Vodka is made with -- you guessed it -- marmalade along with Seville orange peels which are then macerated into their Original Potato Vodka. Then the distillate is redistilled with orange peel from Valencia. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: EAU CLAIRE DISTILLERY PRICKLY PEAR EQUINEOX
THREE OLIVES ROSÉ
DES: Three Olives Rosé combines the taste of rosé wine with the brand's signature vodka. This imported spirit is made from wheat harvested in England. It is available for purchase in the US nationwide.

NAME: HOLY GRASS SCOTTISH VODKA
DES: This flavored vodka is produced at Dunnet Bay Distillers located at Dunnet Head on the northern mainland of Scotland. It is flavored with Holy Grass (aka Bison Grass), Highland apples and apple juice. Holy Grass grows on the banks of the Thurso River near the distillery. Bottled at 41.5% ABV.

NAME: INFUSE SPIRITS CINNAMON APPLE VODKA
DES: This California brand infuses real fruits and spices for their flavored vodka. Starting with their unflavored corn-based vodka, they infuse dried apples and a cinnamon stick for at least 30 days for this bottling. 1.65 g/oz sugar is added. Gluten free. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: 360 MADAGASCAR VANILLA
DES: This vanilla-flavored vodka is made with natural flavors including sugar. The base vodka is made using locally-sourced corn. 360 Vodka is "eco-friendly", their bottle is made from recycled glass, recycled paper, and printed using eco-friendly ink. Bottled at 35% ABV. Try in a latte!

NAME: SVEDKA ORANGE CREAM POP
DES: First launched in 2013, this flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural orange, vanilla, and cream flavors are added. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: SVEDKA VANILLA
DES: This flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural vanilla flavors are added. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: SMIRNOFF PINEAPPLE
DES: This flavored vodka uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. It is infused with natural flavors. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: SMIRNOFF COCONUT
DES: This flavored vodka uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. It is infused with natural flavors. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: SMIRNOFF FLUFFED MARSHMALLOW
DES: First released in 2011, Fluffed Marshmallow is part of Smirnoff's Confections line. It uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. Bottled at 30% ABV.

NAME: SMIRNOFF CRANBERRY
DES: This flavored vodka uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. It is infused with natural cranberry flavors. Bottled at 35% ABV

NAME: SKYY INFUSIONS GEORGIA PEACH
DES: Launched in late 2013, this flavored vodka uses natural peach flavors which are infused into the traditional Skyy Vodka product. Skyy is distilled via four-column distillation from 100% American grains. It uses pure filtered water and is triple-filtered. Made in the USA.

NAME: SKYY INFUSIONS CHERRY
DES: This flavored vodka uses natural cherry flavors which are infused into the traditional Skyy Vodka product. Skyy is distilled via four-column distillation from 100% American grains. It uses pure filtered water and is triple-filtered. Made in the USA.

NAME: SKYY INFUSIONS BLOOD ORANGE
DES: First introduced in 2011, this citrus-flavored vodka uses natural blood orange flavors which are infused into the traditional Skyy Vodka product. Skyy is distilled via four-column distillation from 100% American grains. It uses pure filtered water and is triple-filtered. Made in the USA.

NAME: FINLANDIA NORDIC BERRIES
DES: First launched in 2015, this flavored vodka adds the flavors of lingonberry, cloudberry, and bilberries. It uses the standard Finlandia as its base which is distilled from six-row barley and uses glacial spring water to bring it to proof. Bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: CÎROC AMARETTO
DES: First released in 2013, this is the fourth flavored vodka for CÎROC. They take their grape-based flagship vodka and add amaretto flavors. Cola or pineapple juice are suggested mixers. Bottled at 35% or 37.5% ABV depending on your location.

NAME: ABSOLUT GRÄPE
DES: First released in 2012, This vodka is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka with natural white grape, dragon fruit, and papaya flavors. No sugar added. Bottled at 40% ABV. Previously sold as Absolut Grapevine.

NAME: SKYY INFUSIONS CITRUS
DES: This citrus-flavored vodka uses natural citrus flavors which are infused into the traditional Skyy Vodka product. Skyy is distilled via four-column distillation from 100% American grains. It uses pure filtered water and is triple-filtered. Made in the USA. Skyy Citrus was first launched in 2000 and the name Infusions was added in 2008.

NAME: FINLANDIA GRAPEFRUIT
DES: This flavored vodka uses the standard Finlandia as its base which is distilled from six-row barley and uses glacial spring water to bring it to proof. This grapefruit flavored vodka is made using natural flavors and was introduced to the US in 2007. Formerly known as Grapefruit Fusion, it is bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: CROP ORGANIC CUCUMBER VODKA
DES: Crop Organic Cucumber Vodka is made with USDA certified organic corn grown in the US for the neutral grain base. The cucumber flavored vodka is bottled at 70 proof.

NAME: CHASE OAK SMOKED VODKA
DES: Chase Oak Smoked Vodka is made in Herefordshire by field-to-bottle Chase Distillery. They take water from their own field and then smoke it with English oak for five days. It is then blended with Chase Vodka, a vodka made with three types of potatoes which they grow themselves. The distillery recommends you make a Bloody Mary.

NAME: SVEDKA ROSÉ
DES: Svedka Rosé is a flavored vodka made with 5% rosé wine. Available beginning February 2019, this is the first flavor from Svedka to be sold in a clear glass color to showcase the pink color.

NAME: STOLI CUCUMBER
DES: This cucumber flavored vodka is available beginning late April 2018. Select retailers will have a packet of Tajín chile seasoning affixed to the bottle. Bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: INFUSE SPIRITS LEMON VODKA
DES: This California brand infuses real fruits and spices for their flavored vodka. Starting with their unflavored corn-based vodka, they infuse hand-peeled California Eureka lemons for this product which you can see in the bottle. This gives the vodka a pale yellow color. No sugar added. Gluten free.

NAME: CARDINAL SPIRITS BLACK RASPBERRY BRAMBLE
DES: This concoction starts with Cardinal Spirits grape-derived vodka and adds black raspberries, dried hibiscus, and a touch of agave sugar. Black raspberries are native to North America and a delicious seasonal delicacy.

NAME: 360 HUCKLEBERRY
DES: This huckleberry-flavored vodka is made with natural flavors including sugar. The base vodka is made using locally-sourced corn. 360 Vodka is "eco-friendly", their bottle is made from recycled glass, recycled paper, and printed using eco-friendly ink. Bottled at 35% ABV. Try with lemonade!

NAME: 360 BING CHERRY
DES: Introduced in 2010, this cherry-flavored vodka is made with natural flavors including sugar. The base vodka is made using locally-sourced corn. 360 Vodka is "eco-friendly", their bottle is made from recycled glass, recycled paper, and printed using eco-friendly ink. Bottled at 35% ABV. Try with cola!

NAME: CRATER LAKE SWEET GINGER VODKA
DES: To make their Sweet Ginger Vodka, Crater Lake Spirits sources fresh whole-root ginger. This is then crystallized with sugar cane. No artificial flavors or colors are added before being bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: CRATER LAKE GREEN CHILE VODKA
DES: Crater Lake Spirits only make their Green Chile Vodka after the annual harvest of chiles in Hatch Valley, New Mexico. They roast the chiles along with other peppers and infuse them into their vodka. It is then bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: SVEDKA CUCUMBER LIME
DES: Introduced in 2016, this flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural cucumber and lime flavors are added. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: STOLI CRUSHED RUBY RED GRAPEFRUIT
DES: This Ruby Red Grapefruit flavored vodka is part of Stoli's Crushed series which launched in 2017. Crushed uses real fruit juice and natural flavors. Also note, the makeup of the vodka differs from Stoli's standard and other flavored vodkas. In those, they use wheat and rye, but in Crushed, they use corn and buckwheat which are naturally gluten-free. Bottled at 30% ABV.

NAME: STOLICHNAYA PEACHIK
DES: Peachik is Stoli's peach-flavored vodka. It is grain based (wheat and rye). Bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: STOLICHNAYA STRASBERI
DES: Strasberi is Stoli's strawberry-flavored vodka. It is grain based (wheat and rye). Bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: STOLICHNAYA RAZBERI
DES: This is Stoli's raspberry flavored vodka. Grain based (wheat and rye). Bottled at 37.5% ABV. Try with lemonade and club soda.

NAME: SMIRNOFF SOURCED CRANBERRY APPLE
DES: Sourced Cranberry Apple is part of Smirnoff's line of flavored vodkas which use the standard No. 21 Red Label as its base along with 10% real juice concentrate and natural flavors. No high-fructose sugars are used. Gluten-free. Serve on the rocks or with seltzer. Bottled at 30% ABV. Must be refrigerated after opening

NAME: SMIRNOFF ROOT BEER FLOAT
DES: Root Beer Float is part of Smirnoff's Confections flavored vodka line. It uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. Bottled at 30% ABV.

NAME: SMIRNOFF STRAWBERRY
DES: This flavored vodka uses the classic grain-based No. 21 vodka as its base. It is infused with natural strawberry flavors. Bottled at 35% ABV

NAME: SKYY INFUSIONS WILD STRAWBERRY
DES: Introduced in 2013, this flavored vodka uses natural wild strawberry flavors which are infused into the traditional Skyy Vodka product. Skyy is distilled via four-column distillation from 100% American grains. It uses pure filtered water and is triple-filtered. Made in the USA.

NAME: SKYY INFUSIONS PINEAPPLE
DES: Introduced in 2009, this flavored vodka uses natural pineapple flavors which are infused into the traditional Skyy Vodka product. Skyy is distilled via four-column distillation from 100% American grains. It uses pure filtered water and is triple-filtered. Made in the USA.

NAME: BELVEDERE PEACH NECTAR
DES: Introduced in 2016, this flavored vodka is made by macerating real peaches and apricots into Belvedere's standard rye-based vodka. No sugar or artificial flavors added. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: HANSON OF SONOMA HABANERO VODKA
DES: Based in California’s Sonoma County, Hanson is an organic vodka based on grape distillate. A fifty-plate still creates a very pure spirit that is then filtered seven times. The habanero infusion is made from organic produce. It is non-GMO and gluten free.

NAME: SQUARE ONE CUCUMBER VODKA
DES: This vodka is made using four-column continuous distillation with 100% certified organic American rye. Their water is sourced from the Snake River watershed of the Teton Mountain range. Organic cucumbers are used to infuse the vodka. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: SQUARE ONE BASIL VODKA
DES: This vodka is made using four-column continuous distillation with 100% certified organic American rye. Their water is sourced from the Snake River watershed of the Teton Mountain range. This basil-flavored vodka is made by infusing four types of basil: genovese, Thai, lemon, and sweet. Additionally, coriander, honeysuckle, and lemongrass are also infused. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: BELVEDERE PINK GRAPEFRUIT
DES: Introduced in 2010, Belvedere's Pink Grapefruit is made with real fruit. Pink grapefruits from Spain and Argentina, French ginger, and Spanish lemons are utilized and used to flavor their standard rye-based vodka. It is bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: FIREFLY PEACH MOONSHINE
DES: Firefly Peach Moonshine is a neutral grain spirit naturally flavored with peaches and bottled at 60.9 proof. It's produced by Firefly Distilling and was released in 2013.

NAME: FIREFLY CHERRY MOONSHINE
DES: Released in 2013, this 58.2 proof, cherry-flavored moonshine is produced by Firefly Distilling in South Carolina.

NAME: CÎROC POMEGRANATE
DES: CÎROC Pomegranate is made with the brand's standard grape-based vodka for its base. This limited edition pomegranate-flavored vodka is available as of October 2021 while supplies last.

NAME: FRANKLY ORGANIC APPLE VODKA
DES: Frankly Organic Vodka is made from non-GMO organic corn. It is gluten free and certified Kosher. The brand is based in Austin, Texas where the product is bottled and they list all ingredients used on their back labels. For their Apple version, they use organic ingredients such as apples, ginger root, lemon juice, cayenne, wild cherry bark, and Vermont Grade A maple syrup.

NAME: VEIL BOTANIC COLLECTION GRAPEFRUIT AND ROSE
SMIRNOFF SORBET LIGHT RASPBERRY POMEGRANATE
DES: Smirnoff Sorbet Light Raspberry Pomegranate is infused with delicate flavor notes of sweet yet tart raspberries and juicy pomegranates with a cool, refreshing finish. With only 78 calories per 1.5 oz., this spirit pairs perfectly with club soda, ginger ale, or cranberry juice. For an elevated serve, try in your go-to Cosmo recipe.

NAME: PURITY SPRITZ MEDITERRANEAN CITRUS
DES: Purity Spritz Mediterranean Citrus is a flavored vodka using the brand's Purity Signature 34 Edition Organic Vodka as its base. It is flavored with Bergamot, grapefruit, orange, and other botanicals and contains no artificial flavors or sweeteners. The brand recommends a 50:50 serving of Purity Spritz and bubbles of your choice (Champagne, Prosecco, soda, etc.) Bottled at 30% ABV.

NAME: THREE OLIVES ELVIS PRESLEY COCONUT WATER
MICRO BATCH VODKA RASPBERRY & BLACK PEPPER LIQUEUR
PASSION FRUIT SMALL BATCH ISLAND VODKA
SMIRNOFF ZERO SUGAR INFUSIONS CUCUMBER & LIME
DES: This spirit is part of Smirnoff's line of sugar-free vodka infusions. This release is infused with natural flavors of cucumber and lime. It is bottled at a 30% ABV.

NAME: LAST MOUNTAIN SWEET TEA FLAVOURED VODKA
LAST MOUNTAIN DILL PICKLE FLAVOURED VODKA
CHASE RHUBARB VODKA
DES: Chase Rhubarb Vodka is made at the field-to-bottle Chase Distillery in Herefordshire. This rhubarb-flavored vodka was initially only a limited edition release but is now a permanent part of its portfolio. It is made using the distillery's classic Potato Vodka as the base to which locally-grown rhubarb macerates and then is re-distilled. Post-distillation fresh rhubarb macerates again giving the vodka a pink tint.

NAME: PUR VODKA SERIE AUTOGRAPHE 01 MICHEL JODOIN
GREY GOOSE LA VANILLE
DES: Grey Goose La Vanille returned to the US and UK in September 2018, 15 years after its first introduction. It is made using the standard Grey Goose winter wheat vodka base and natural vanilla flavor sourced from beans harvested in Madagascar. No sugar added.

NAME: MISSISSIPPI RIVER DISTILLING COMPANY, PRIDE OF THE WAPSI
BELVEDERE GINGER ZEST
DES: Available beginning April 2018, this flavored extension from Belvedere is made with ginger, lemon, and a touch of grapefruit. These ingredients are macerated into their 100% non-GMO Polish rye vodka. It is 100% natural with no sugar added.

NAME: DRIPPING SPRINGS TEXAS ORANGE
DES: This orange-flavored vodka is made by steeping hand-zested Texas oranges into Dripping Springs Vodka and redistilling it. The base vodka is made from Midwestern non-GMO corn and is gluten free. It is also certified Kosher by the Houston Kashruth Association.

NAME: SEAGRAM'S JUICY WATERMELON
DES: Introduced in summer 2017, this watermelon-flavored vodka is made with by adding natural flavors to Seagram's Extra Smooth Vodka, made from American grains.

NAME: ARBIKIE CHILLI VODKA
DES: This flavored vodka is made using chipotle chiles grown in Scotland by Scotland’s first chile farm, Chillilicious. Arbikie infuses the chiles in their field-to-bottle potato vodka. Bottled at 43% ABV.

NAME: ART IN THE AGE CHICORY ROOT VODKA
DES: This is part of Tamworth’s Art in the Age line of limited bottles. An expression that harkens back to the days when chicory was used to stretch coffee supplies. A vodka flavored with whole chicory root, dandelion root, cinnamon, and maple syrup.

NAME: 360 GEORGIA PEACH
DES: This peach-flavored vodka is made with natural flavors including sugar. The base vodka is made using locally-sourced corn. 360 Vodka is "eco-friendly", their bottle is made from recycled glass, recycled paper, and printed using eco-friendly ink. Bottled at 35% ABV. Try with pink lemonade!

NAME: 360 RED DELICIOUS APPLE
DES: This apple-flavored vodka is made with natural flavors including sugar. The base vodka is made using locally-sourced corn. 360 Vodka is "eco-friendly", their bottle is made from recycled glass, recycled paper, and printed using eco-friendly ink. Bottled at 35% ABV. Try with cranberry juice!

NAME: 360 SORRENTO LEMON
DES: Introduced in 2010, this lemon-flavored vodka is made with natural flavors including sugar. The base vodka is made using locally-sourced corn. 360 Vodka is "eco-friendly", their bottle is made from recycled glass, recycled paper, and printed using eco-friendly ink. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: SVEDKA PEACH
DES: Introduced in 2014, this flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural peach flavors are added. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: SVEDKA GRAPEFRUIT JALAPEÑO
DES: First launched in 2015, this flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural grapefruit and jalapeño flavors are added. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: SVEDKA CHERRY
DES: This flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural cherry flavors are added. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: SVEDKA CLEMENTINE
DES: This flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural clementine flavors are added. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: STOLICHNAYA CITROS
DES: Citros is Stoli's citrus-flavored vodka made from the oils of a variety of lemons and limes. The vodka is grain based (wheat and rye). Bottled at 37.5% ABV.

NAME: SMIRNOFF SOURCED RUBY RED GRAPEFRUIT
DES: Sourced Ruby Red Grapefruit is part of Smirnoff's line of flavored vodkas which use the standard No. 21 Red Label as its base along with 10% real juice concentrate and natural flavors. No high-fructose sugars are used. Gluten-free. Serve on the rocks or with seltzer. Bottled at 30% ABV. Must be refrigerated after opening

NAME: SKYY INFUSIONS TROPICAL MANGO
DES: Launched in 2016, this flavored vodka uses natural mango and other flavors which are infused into the traditional Skyy Vodka product. Skyy is distilled via four-column distillation from 100% American grains. It uses pure filtered water and is triple-filtered.

NAME: SKYY INFUSIONS HONEYCRISP APPLE
DES: First introduced in 2016, this flavored vodka uses natural honeycrisp apple and other flavors which are infused into the traditional Skyy Vodka product. Skyy is distilled via four-column distillation from 100% American grains. It uses pure filtered water and is triple-filtered. Made in the USA.

NAME: BELVEDERE CITRUS
DES: This flavored vodka is made with three separate macerations: one with Italian lemons, one with Argentine lemons, and one with Mexican limes. The vodka itself is rye-based. No artificial flavors and no sugar added. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: BELVEDERE MANGO PASSION
DES: First introduced in 2014, this flavored vodka is made by macerating mango, passion fruit, tangerines, and lime into Belvedere's standard rye-based vodka. No artificial flavors or sugar is added. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: HANSON OF SONOMA GINGER VODKA
DES: Based in California’s Sonoma County, Hanson is an organic vodka based on grape distillate. A fifty-plate still creates a very pure spirit that is then filtered seven times. The ginger infusion is made from organic produce. It is non-GMO and gluten free.

NAME: ABSOLUT ÄPPLE
DES: First released in 2011, this vodka is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka with natural red apple and ginger flavor. No sugar added. Bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: ABSOLUT CILANTRO
DES: First released in 2013, this vodka is made using Absolut's standard winter-wheat-based vodka with natural cilantro and lime flavor. No sugar added.

NAME: HANSON OF SONOMA CUCUMBER VODKA
DES: Based in California’s Sonoma County, Hanson is an organic vodka based on grape distillate. A fifty-plate still creates a very pure spirit that is then filtered seven times. The cucumber infusion is created with organic cucumbers. It is non-GMO and gluten free.

NAME: OYO BARREL-FINISHED HONEY VANILLA BEAN VODKA
DES: What a mouthful of a name! This vodka starts with Ohio red winter wheat that is distilled a whopping 34 times. This is infused with local wildflower honey and organic, single-source, fair-trade vanilla beans. Lastly, the spirit enjoys up to a year in a barrel that formerly held the distillery’s bourbon.

NAME: SPRING44 HONEY FLAVORED VODKA
DES: Spring 44 seeks to harness the purity of their water source in their Colorado-born spirits. The spring is located in Buckhorn Canyon at 2,000 feet elevation and surrounded by 160,000 acres of National forest. For this flavored vodka, the grain vodka base is infused with Colorado honey lending an attractive golden tone to the spirit.

NAME: PEARL LIME BASIL VODKA
DES: Pearl Vodka is a Canadian project focused on making classic, smooth vodkas. Wheat from Alberta is distilled five times and cut with water from the Canadian Rockies. The resulting spirit is repeatedly filtered for an easy, highly mixable style. This bottling marries the complimentary flavors of lime and basil.

NAME: BATCH 206 MAD MINT VODKA
DES: Batch 206 is owned and operated by Jeff Steichen and his wife Daleen. They source grain and mint from Washington to make this vodka. It is also slightly sweetened with Pacific Northwest beet sugar. This is bottled at 100 proof.

NAME: FIREFLY BLACKBERRY MOONSHINE
DES: This neutral grain spirit flavored with blackberries is a product of Firefly Distillery. Firefly Blackberry Moonshine is now available nationwide, but initially could only be purchased at the distillery in Wadmalaw Island, South Carolina.

NAME: FIREFLY CARAMEL MOONSHINE
DES: This 60-proof neutral grain spirit is flavored and colored with caramel. Released in 2013, it's one of the flavored moonshines from Firefly Distilling in South Carolina.

NAME: THREE OLIVES DUDE. LEMON-LIME FLAVORED VODKA
FRANKLY ORGANIC GRAPEFRUIT VODKA
DES: Frankly Organic Vodka is made from non-GMO organic corn. It is gluten free and certified Kosher. The brand is based in Austin, Texas where the product is bottled and they list all ingredients used on their back labels. For their Grapefruit version, they use organic ingredients such as ruby red grapefruit, apples, Ceylon cinnamon, lemon juice, Vermont Grade A maple syrup, and maca root from the Peruvian Central Andes.

NAME: FRANKLY ORGANIC STRAWBERRY VODKA
DES: Frankly Organic Vodka is made from non-GMO organic corn. It is gluten free and certified Kosher. The brand is based in Austin, Texas where the product is bottled and they list all ingredients used on their back labels. For the Strawberry version, they use organic ingredients such as strawberries, apples, turmeric, coconut water, lemon juice, Vermont Grade A maple syrup, wild cherry bark, and ginger root.

NAME: VING KALE, LEMON PEEL & CUCUMBER VODKA
DES: VING Vodka is made from organic, non-GMO corn. For this bottling, organic kale, lemon peel, and cucumber were infused in the vodka before bottling. Made in California, it is gluten-free and there are no added sugar or other additives. VING Vodka is a women-owned and women-led company.

NAME: BELVEDERE ORGANIC INFUSIONS BLACKBERRY & LEMONGRASS
DES: For the Belvedere Organic Infusions range, Belvedere Vodka sought out 100% certified organic fruits, spices and botanicals with no additives or synthetic flavors. It is made with 100% organic rye grown in Poland. This one features blackberry and lemongrass with a touch of sage. It is available as of May, 2021.

NAME: BELVEDERE ORGANIC INFUSIONS PEAR & GINGER
DES: For the Belvedere Organic Infusions range, Belvedere Vodka sought out 100% certified organic fruits, spices and botanicals with no additives or synthetic flavors. It is made with 100% organic rye grown in Poland. This one features pear and ginger with a touch of linden honey. It is available as of May, 2021.

NAME: BELVEDERE ORGANIC INFUSIONS LEMON & BASIL
DES: For the Belvedere Organic Infusions range, Belvedere Vodka sought out 100% certified organic fruits, spices and botanicals with no additives or synthetic flavors. It is made with 100% organic rye grown in Poland. This one features lemon and basil with a touch of elderberry. It is available as of May, 2021.

NAME: SVEDKA CHERRY LIMEADE
DES: This flavor in the brand's lineup is meant to "provide a summer mindset in just one sip". It is available in both 750 ML and 1 L bottles, and is available as of May, 2021.

NAME: ABSOLUT WATERMELON
DES: This watermelon-flavored vodka is made with no added sugar and is bottled at 76 proof. It is available as of April 2021.

NAME: THE NEWFOUNDLAND DISTILLERY CO RHUBARB VODKA
SVEDKA PURE INFUSIONS DRAGONFRUIT MELON
DES: Svedka Pure Infusions Dragonfruit Melon is infused with natural flavors and zero sugar. Bottled at 30% ABV, this flavored vodka launched in June 2020.

NAME: SVEDKA PURE INFUSIONS GINGER LIME
DES: Svedka Pure Infusions Ginger Lime is infused with natural flavors and zero sugar. Bottled at 30% ABV, this flavored vodka launched in June 2020.

NAME: FRUITLAND AUGUSTA GEORGIA PEACH TEA VODKA
MOUNTAIN VIEW DISTILLERY DAVID’S HARP CITRON VODKA
RE:FIND CUCUMBER FLAVORED VODKA
DES: Re:Find Cucumber Flavored Vodka is made using cucumbers grown by family farmers in Arroyo Grande, California. During the growing season, cucumbers are harvested, delivered and juiced the same day. The cucumber juice is added to the distillery's grape-based vodka. No carbon-filtration takes place.

NAME: SALTWORKS PROPERTY SMOKED SEA SALT VODKA
DES: Saltworks Property Smoked Sea Salt Vodka is a flavored vodka produced by Boston Brands of Maine, owned by The Sazerac Co. This is one of two salt-infused vodkas released by the brand which were introduced in early 2019. Bottled at 80 proof.

NAME: SALTWORKS PROPERTY HIMALAYAN PINK SALT VODKA
DES: Saltworks Property Himalayan Pink Salt Vodka is a flavored vodka produced by Boston Brands of Maine, owned by The Sazerac Co. The vodka is infused with salt minded in the Himalayan Mountains. Bottled at 80 proof.

NAME: ABSOLUT VODKA ANDY WARHOL LIMITED EDITION
CROP ORGANIC TOMATO VODKA
DES: Crop Organic Tomato Vodka is made with USDA certified organic corn grown in the US for the neutral grain base. The Tomato flavored vodka is bottled at 70 proof. Note: This product has been discontinued.

NAME: SKYY INFUSIONS COLD BREW COFFEE
DES: This cold-brew inspired vodka uses Arabica coffee beans which are infused into the traditional Skyy Vodka product. Skyy is distilled via four-column distillation from 100% American grains. It uses pure filtered water and is triple-filtered.

NAME: EFFEN YUZU CITRUS VODKA
DES: EFFEN Yuzu Citrus Vodka is a flavored vodka from the Dutch brand released in April 2019. Yuzu is a fragrant citrus fruit with origins in China, but it is widely cultivated in Japan. Its flavor is described as a cross between grapefruit and lemon. EFFEN Yuzu Citrus is made with its standard 100% French wheat neutral spirit base. No added sugar or artificial flavors are used in its production.

NAME: EFFEN ROSÉ VODKA
DES: EFFEN Rosé is a flavored vodka from the Dutch brand released in April 2019. It is made with its standard 100% French wheat neutral spirit base. No added sugar or artificial flavors are used in its production. This Rosé flavor is suggested to serve with club soda or sparkling wine.

NAME: LAST MOUNTAIN SWEET SASKATOON BERRY VODKA
ENCHANTED ROCK TEXAS VODKA, PEACH FLAVORED
SEAGRAM'S GOLDEN APRICOT
DES: Introduced in late 2016, this Golden Apricot Flavored Vodka is made by adding natural flavors to Seagram's Extra Smooth Vodka, made from American grains. Bottled at 35% ABV.

NAME: 500,000 SCOVILLES NAGA CHILLI VODKA
DES: Bottled by The Hot Enough Vodka Co. in England, this flavored vodka uses Naga Jolokia chillies (also called ghost peppers). The Scoville scale is a way to measure the hotness or pungency level in a pepper. For reference, a jalapeño ranks from 2,500-8,000 on the scale and a habanero ranges from 100,000-350,000. Bottled in 20cl sized bottles at 80 proof.

NAME: ARBIKIE STRAWBERRY VODKA
DES: This flavored vodka is made by infusing fresh strawberries into Arbikie's estate-grown potato vodka. Each vintage will vary slightly as each crop varies. Sold in 500ml bottles at 50% ABV. Limited availability.

NAME: ART IN THE AGE SWEET POTATO VODKA
DES: This is part of Tamworth’s Art in the Age line of limited bottles. Their Sweet Potato Vodka is infused with whole sweet potatoes, white oak chips, cloves, and maple syrup. Bottled in 375ml sized bottles.

NAME: ART IN THE AGE BEET ROOT VODKA
DES: This is part of Tamworth’s Art in the Age line of limited bottles. This expression is a tribute to the yields of a New Hampshire autumn. This vodka is flavored with a blend of sweet beets, cranberries, apple pomace. Later tarragon, honey, and salt are added as well. Despite all these additions the vodka is still bottled at 40% ABV.

NAME: FLYING PEPPER TOBAGO PEPPER VODKA
DES: Made by the Fair Game Beverage Co. in Pittsboro, North Carolina, this flavored vodka is made with North Carolina-grown tobago pepper also called ají dulce, a smoky, sweet, and mildly hot pepper. They infuse these peppers in an organic soft red wheat vodka which they source from TOPO Distillery in Chapel Hill. Bottled at 80 proof.

NAME: CASCADE ALCHEMY CHAI TEA FLAVORED VODKA
DES: This creative flavored vodka starts with Cascade Alchemy’s super-filtered grain-based vodka. A cocktail of black tea and eastern spices macerate in the finished vodka to suggest the soothing flavors of the coffeehouse favorite chai tea.

NAME: 44 NORTH SUNNYSLOPE NECTARINE
DES: This nectarine-flavored vodka uses the brand's unflavored vodka made from potatoes as its base. That is distilled from 100% Idaho potatoes, Burbank and Russet, and is naturally gluten-free. It is brought down to 35% ABV using Rocky Mountain water. 44 North is named for the latitude that crosses through Idaho. Try with iced tea!

NAME: 360 GLAZED DONUT
DES: This donut-flavored vodka is made with natural flavors including sugar. The base vodka is made using locally-sourced corn. 360 Vodka is "eco-friendly", their bottle is made from recycled glass, recycled paper, and printed using eco-friendly ink. Bottled at 35% ABV. Try with iced coffee!

NAME: 360 GRAPE
DES: This grape-flavored vodka is made with natural flavors including sugar. The base vodka is made using locally-sourced corn. 360 Vodka is "eco-friendly", their bottle is made from recycled glass, recycled paper, and printed using eco-friendly ink. Bottled at 35% ABV. Try with lemon-lime soda and grape juice!

NAME: 360 RED RASPBERRY
DES: This raspberry-flavored vodka is made with natural flavors including sugar. The base vodka is made using locally-sourced corn. 360 Vodka is "eco-friendly", their bottle is made from recycled glass, recycled paper, and printed using eco-friendly ink. Bottled at 35% ABV. Try with cider!

NAME: 360 MANGO
DES: This mango-flavored vodka is made with natural flavors including sugar. The base vodka is made using locally-sourced corn. 360 Vodka is "eco-friendly", their bottle is made from recycled glass, recycled paper, and printed using eco-friendly ink. Bottled at 35% ABV. Use instead of rum in a mojito!

NAME: SVEDKA COLADA
DES: Introduced in 2012, this flavored vodka uses Svedka's standard vodka as its base which is column-distilled from Swedish winter wheat. Natural coconut, pineapple, and mango flavors are added. Bottled at 35% ABV.
